description.narrative:
Existing CBDN members, 10 CSOs from Armenia, Azerbaijan and Georgia as well as Abkhazia, Nagorny Karabakh and South Ossetia and new members;

CSOs and experts in the field of economic cooperation;

National and local authorities in Armenia, Azerbaijan and Georgia (de jure) as well as Abkhazia, Nagorny Karabakh and South Ossetia (de facto) ; 

Economic and business structures including Chambers of Commerce, sectoral associations, etc;  

Businesses and economic actors; and  

SMEs in selected sectors (Tea producers, Beekeeping, Tourism, dairy sectors)
